title: S13 Ep81: The Lost Journals of Nikola Tesla: Time Travel, Alternative Energy and the Secret of Nazi Flying Saucers
itunes:title: The Lost Journals of Nikola Tesla: Time Travel, Alternative Energy and the Secret of Nazi Flying Saucers
description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS blows the dust off of The Lost Journals of Nikola Tesla: Time Travel, Alternative Energy and the Secret of Nazi Flying Saucers with guest
Tim Swartz.

Shortly After his death at an advanced age in a NYC hotel room in 1943, many of Tesla's most important unpublished patents and papers went missing. Today we go inside the mind of a mad genius to uncover mysteries of Time, Space and the Supernatural.

Get the book here: www.Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio.com
